# Static Forms — https://www.staticforms.dev/
# Free: 500 submissions/month.
#
# Paste the FORM API key from: Forms → your form → General (sf_…)
# Set delivery email in the Static Forms dashboard (e.g. contact@runtosolve.com)
#
# SECURITY (required — the form key is always visible in the browser):
#   Forms → Security → Domain restriction → allow ONLY:
#     - localhost (for npm run dev)
#     - your GitHub Pages host, e.g. <user>.github.io
#   Optionally enable CAPTCHA. Keep Spam filter on Standard.
#   Docs: https://www.staticforms.dev/docs/account/api-key
#
# Restart the dev server after changing this file.
# For production, also add the same value as a GitHub Actions secret:
#   VITE_STATICFORMS_API_KEY
VITE_STATICFORMS_API_KEY=
